OL,3,CTributes to crash victim who was the
OL,4,C'life and soul of every gathering'
OL,6,FThe family of a woman who died
OL,7,Ffollowing a crash in North Somerset
OL,8,Fhas paid tribute to her, describing
OL,9,Fher as the "life and soul of every
OL,10,Fgathering".
OL,12,FKarina Haselgrove-Spurin, 50, was
OL,13,Fwalking on High Street, Portbury, when
OL,14,Fshe was involved in a collision with a
OL,15,Fcar on Sunday 22 February.
OL,17,FShe was taken to hospital, where she
OL,18,Fdied the next day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
