OL,3,CTributes to crash victim who was the
OL,4,C'life and soul of every gathering'
OL,6,FKarina's family said: "We are
OL,7,Fheartbroken to lose our beloved Karina
OL,8,Fso tragically.
OL,10,F"Karina was a caring and loyal friend
OL,11,Fto many. She was the life and soul of
OL,12,Fevery gathering and cherished the
OL,13,Fpeople around her deeply."
OL,15,FThey added: "She was adventurous at
OL,16,Fheart, always travelling, exploring,
OL,17,Fand finding joy in the outdoors.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772549421
OL,3,CTributes to crash victim who was the
OL,4,C'life and soul of every gathering'
OL,6,F"She is dearly loved and deeply
OL,7,Fmissed, but her spirit, her laughter,
OL,8,Fand the love she gave so freely will
OL,9,Fstay with us always."
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police said
OL,12,Fenquiries are continuing into what
OL,13,Fhappened.
OL,15,FA man, in his 50s, is due to attend a
OL,16,Fvoluntary police interview in the near
OL,17,Ffuture, police said.
OL,19,FThe force is appealing for anyone with
OL,20,Finformation, or anyone who saw what
OL,21,Fhappened, to come forward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
